<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>[SHOTS FIRED! SHOTS FIRED! ANYBODY GOT A LOCATION?]</p>
<p>[THIS IS SITE-81 COMMAND. CONFIRM, FIRE AND LOCATION?]</p>
<p>[F-PATROL, CAN CONFIRM. ONE SHOT. SOUNDED LIKE SUB-LEVEL IN ADMIN.]</p>
<p>[COMMAND, MOVING TOWARD STAIRS TO INTERCEPT POTENTIAL HOSTILES.]</p>
<p>[G-PATROL ALSO INBOUND, TAKING ELEVATOR.]</p>
<p>[COPY.]</p>
</div>
<p><br />
<br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<p>The guard went to key up their own radio, when very suddenly the lights in the armory went out.</p>
