<p><br /></p>
<p>The purple avatar floated on the screen stargin back at Umber. Of all the things he had to deal with right now, he was not wanting to deal with the dopey computer person on the other side of the glass.</p>
<p>Umber then groaned.</p>
<p>Loudly.</p>
<p>Loud enough that it echoed off the walls of the shielded chamber and hung in the air like a fart in church. &quot;Shadjar! Why can't you just go away?&quot;</p>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="margin: auto; overflow: auto; padding: 0px 10px; width: 350px; height: 240px; background-color: #faf4f2; border-style: solid; border-width: 20px 5px 5px 5px; border-color: #b1e2f0; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;">
